<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Happy Birthday ❤️</title>

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#ffffff;
color:#333;
text-align:center;
}

.hero{
height:100vh;
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
padding:20px;
}

h1{
font-size:3rem;
color:#d46a92;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.subtitle{
max-width:700px;
font-size:1.2rem;
line-height:1.8;
}

.btn{
margin-top:25px;
padding:15px 30px;
background:#d46a92;
color:white;
border:none;
border-radius:30px;
cursor:pointer;
}

section{
padding:80px 20px;
}

.memory{
max-width:900px;
margin:auto;
}

.memory h2{
color:#d46a92;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.final{
display:none;
padding:80px 20px;
}

.heart{
font-size:3rem;
animation:beat 1s infinite;
}

@keyframes beat{
50%{transform:scale(1.2);}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="hero">
<h1>Happy Birthday ❤️</h1>

<p class="subtitle">
Today is all about you. I made this little surprise just for you.
</p>

<button class="btn" onclick="document.getElementById('msg').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">
Start Your Surprise
</button>
</div>

<section class="memory" id="msg">

<h2>A Little Message For You ❤️</h2>

<p style="line-height:2; max-width:800px; margin:auto;">

You have been through so much lately, and I know things haven't always been easy.
<br><br>

I just wanted you to know that you are loved, appreciated, and deeply special to me.
I hope this birthday brings you happiness, peace, and everything your heart deserves.
<br><br>

You are truly one of the most wonderful people anyone could ever have in their life.
Being with you showed me what love really feels like, and every day with you makes me grateful that I get to love someone as incredible as you.
<br><br>

You became the reason behind so many of my smiles, the person I look forward to talking to every day, and the person I imagine my future with.
<br><br>

I keep dreaming about the day we finally build our home together and get to share all the little moments of life side by side.
<br><br>

If there is one thing I wish for more than anything in this world, it's a lifetime with you.
I love you more than anything.
<br><br>

Thank you for being my favorite person and my home.
<br><br>

Happy Birthday, my love. ❤️

</p>
</section>

<section style="padding:80px 20px;">
<h2 style="color:#d46a92;">Our Memories ❤️</h2>

<img src="photo1.jpg" style="width:250px;border-radius:20px;margin:10px;">
<img src="photo2.jpg" style="width:250px;border-radius:20px;margin:10px;">
<img src="photo3.jpg" style="width:250px;border-radius:20px;margin:10px;">
</section>

<div style="padding:80px 20px;">
<div class="heart">❤️</div>
<h2>You Did It!</h2>
<p>Happy Birthday ❤️</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
